.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613c6d6eaee29aff0c1c037b1a3b98238cf67044","tid":1097383,"uid":132038,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92453b6e0d9d585f88ba3da5b1dd5e0c695230ac","tid":1097383,"uid":22362,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"林榮基呢單嘢冇煲大真係錯失良機<br />\n明明有晒證據有晒人證<br />\n可以話出師有利<br />\n比起魚蛋革命 雨傘都更加有機會大搞<br />\n可惜冇人出到黎lead到大家<br />\n可能經過呢幾次運動已經冇人肯出黎了"},{"pid":"0ecc2f0c820d9e3dd92f0a78b3b1bf424ed1a293","tid":1097383,"uid":34154,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170830/s00001/ed5d057db8b8951b193c8476e01b4875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170830%2Fs00001%2Fed5d057db8b8951b193c8476e01b4875.jpg&h=4ce14ff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"426c8098c7206e6aa1518c7e971bb1d3204ad23c","tid":1097383,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:24:45.000Z","msg":"3年間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地個鐘行得快過佢3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5172227a8ebcf7f953b7c48e2ab86c342cd885","tid":1097383,"uid":238628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"依家香港人只係諗緊點樣快d移民,根本就冇諗過要救香港<br />\n<br />\n但係又唔可以怪佢地,因為香港已經冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4b1918ee869aba2859b7d896836369fdcc45fe","tid":1097383,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"可唔可以帶埋我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想做政冶犯"},{"pid":"b6071b086149af85b5d57eeb80a89b35971a5886","tid":1097383,"uid":1425,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"正廢老,